      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Ciclo Report Program : Esecuzione per inizio ciclo        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prn-ini-cic-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di interruzione forzata    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-prn-flg-int      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione totali generali                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-gen-tot-stc      .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-gen-tot-ini      .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-gen-tot-ind      .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-gen-tot-amm      .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-gen-tot-res      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Intestazione foglio                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   int-pag-sta-000      thru int-pag-sta-999        .
       prn-ini-cic-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Ciclo Report Program : Esecuzione per fine ciclo          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prn-fin-cic-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di interruzione forzata    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-prn-flg-int      .
       prn-fin-cic-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa totali generali                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da stampare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tot-gen-tot-stc    not  > 1
                     go to prn-fin-cic-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se righe residue sufficienti           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        p-res                >    4
                     go to prn-fin-cic-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Reintestazione                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   int-pag-sta-000      thru int-pag-sta-999        .
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-fin-cic-999.
       prn-fin-cic-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * 1. linea per totale                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Interlinea                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sottolineatura                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   prn-stl-det-000      thru prn-stl-det-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * 2. linea per totale generale                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
